<p>
Zentus Focus: <br/>
Zentus is a project that born when we realizing that the learning of some math branches it is only practicing. Zentus based
on this and in the new technologies start this big project. 
Zentus focus is that the 2-7 years old kids can learn with a very different and funny manner aplying the top technologies in the market.
What consist zentus project? Zentus project is a software that recognized the human body through a kinect making this part so funny.
Then, the software start to playing the different educational games that the kid is going to answer shaking his body. The games 
are the next: Geometry, Math.
In this globalized world all the people need to know how to use the technologies to challenge in their lifes. 
Zentus goal is that the kids familiarize with the technologies in a early age of their lifes. 
</p>

